Prototype : https://govern-predict.lovable.app/?utm_source=lovable-editor

GovAI Insight Platform is an AI-powered governance solution that unifies data from multiple departments to deliver real-time insights, predictive analytics, and automated alerts. It helps governments make proactive, data-driven decisions, improving citizen services and transparency.

Built with Flutter, Django, and AI/ML models, it ensures data privacy, scalability, and compliance.
✅ Predictive governance
✅ AI chat assistant
✅ Secure, modular, and citizen-centric platform
